---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
import CopyButton from "../components/CopyButton.astro";
---

<Base title="Getting Started" description="How to install Claude Code plugins from skill7 marketplace">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">Getting Started</h1>
  <p class="mt-2 text-lg text-gray-600">Install Claude Code plugins in three steps.</p>

  <!-- Prerequisites -->
  <div class="mt-6 rounded-lg border border-amber-200 bg-amber-50 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-amber-800">
    <strong>Prerequisite:</strong> Claude Code CLI must be installed.
    <a href="https://docs.anthropic.com/en/docs/claude-code/overview" class="underline hover:text-amber-900" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
      Install Claude Code
    </a>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-10 space-y-12">
    <section>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">1. What are Claude Code plugins?</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-gray-700">
        Plugins extend Claude Code with custom commands, specialized agents, domain skills, and lifecycle hooks.
        They're open source, installable via CLI, and work with any project.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">2. Add the marketplace</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-gray-700">
        Register the heurema emporium marketplace:
      </p>
      <div class="mt-4">
        <CopyButton text="claude plugin marketplace add heurema/emporium" />
      </div>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-500">
        Run once. After that, all plugins in the catalog become installable.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">3. Install a plugin</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-gray-700">
        Browse the catalog, pick a plugin, and install it:
      </p>
      <div class="mt-4">
        <CopyButton text="claude plugin install sigil@emporium" />
      </div>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-500">
        The plugin is now active in your Claude Code sessions.
      </p>
    </section>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-12">
    <a href="/" class="btn-primary">Browse Plugins</a>
  </div>
</Base>
